26px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;例：设f(x)=x^2,求<img src="http://img.blog.csdn.net/20130601152116187" alt="" style="border-style: none; border-width: initial; max-width: 100%;"/></span></p><p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 解：<img src="http://img.blog.csdn.net/20130601152209904" alt="" style="border-style: none; border-width: initial; max-width: 100%;"/></span></p><p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><em><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">1)随机投点法计算定积分</span></strong></em></p><p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;基本思想是在矩形区域上</span><em><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">随机均匀的投点实现</span></strong></em><span style="font-size: 18px;">。本算法的基本思想是在积分区间上随机均匀的产生点, 即在[a,b]上随机均匀的取点, 求出由这些点产生的函数值的</span><em><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">算术平均值, 再乘以区间宽度</span></strong></em><span style="font-size: 18px;">, 即可解出定积分得近似解</span><img src="http://img.blog.csdn.net/20130601151928425" alt="" style="border-style: none; border-width: initial; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; text-align: center;"/>。</p><p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://img.blog.csdn.net/20130601152936686" alt="" style="border-style: none; border-width: initial; max-width: 100%;"/><br/></p><p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 算法具体代码如下：</span></p><p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"></span></p><div class="dp-highlighter b